Description: philsf's medical statistics toolkit
 Metapackage for an R-based environment for statistical analysis.
 .
 It assumes R packages are installed directly from CRAN rather than
 native .deb packages, providing the system headers and development
 tools required to compile from source. This configuration supports
 clinical research workflows for epidemiologists and biostatisticians.
